  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Weatherwax\" title=\"House Weatherwax\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Anya Weatherwax</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Weatherwax\" title=\"House Weatherwax\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Anya_Weatherwax_by_Riotarttherite.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Anya Weatherwax by Riotarttherite.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Anya_Weatherwax_by_Riotarttherite.png/350px-Anya_Weatherwax_by_Riotarttherite.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Anya_Weatherwax_by_Riotarttherite.png/525px-Anya_Weatherwax_by_Riotarttherite.png 1.5x, /images/2/24/Anya_Weatherwax_by_Riotarttherite.png 2x\" /></a><div>Anya by © <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://riotarttherite.tumblr.com/\">Riotarttherite</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Weatherwax\" title=\"House Weatherwax\">House Weatherwax</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_126_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">126&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-calc-Anya_Weatherwax_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-calc-Anya_Weatherwax-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Anya Weatherwax</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Weatherwax\" title=\"House Weatherwax\">House Weatherwax</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anya_Weatherwax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_Ball\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day Ball\">Maiden's Day Ball</a> was held at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> to find a second wife and new queen for King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>. Many <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maidens</a> across <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> came to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> in hopes of marrying the young king. However, the event was not a true ball, but merely a procession of maidens, each woman curtsying before the king while a <a href=\"/index.php/Herald\" title=\"Herald\">herald</a> announced her name and lineage. Anya, only seven years old, was one of these maidens. She informed King Aegon that her <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a> was named Twinklehoof, and that she loved him very much. When Anya asked the king if he had a good horse, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a> grew impatient with her, and told her that \"His Grace has a hundred horses\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anya_Weatherwax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-calc-Anya_Weatherwax-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-calc-Anya_Weatherwax_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Anya_Weatherwax\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Anya Weatherwax</a> calculation.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404003138\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.071 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.255 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 589/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10584/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6527/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1224/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1498/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.75 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  243.222      1 -total\n 95.66%  232.663      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.17%  231.465      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.46%   25.451     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.37%    8.189      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.49%    6.045      2 Template:Ref\n  2.46%    5.977      2 Template:Date\n  1.72%    4.172      2 Template:Ref/core\n  1.64%    3.996      1 Template:Ref_calculation\n  0.70%    1.705      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25184-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404003138 and revision id 321193\n -->\n",
